Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:09.37,zh,,0,0,0,,撑着点，瑞克，已经快到了\N{\ren}C'mon, Rick. We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:11.66,zh,,0,0,0,,别管我，莫蒂，这是唯一的办法\N{\ren}Leave me, Morty. It's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:14.21,zh,,0,0,0,,什么…\N{\ren}What... Were... What... Were we...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.34,zh,,0,0,0,,我们是刀锋战士吗？真酷\N{\ren}Were we Blades in that one? That's fucking tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:17.80,zh,,0,0,0,,撑着点\N{\ren}Just stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.44,zh,,0,0,0,,我好怕，莫蒂，我能看到终点了\N{\ren}I'm... I'm scared, Morty. I can see the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.49,zh,,0,0,0,,我太傻了，我太渺小了\N{\ren}I'm a silly man. I'm a silly, small man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.32,zh,,0,0,0,,很抱歉把你扯进来\N{\ren}I'm... I'm sorry I got you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.46,zh,,0,0,0,,让我来解决这个问题，如何？\N{\ren}Then how about I get us outta this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:43.33,zh,,0,0,0,,－喂？　－嘿，洁西卡\N{\ren}- Hello? - Hey, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.92,zh,,0,0,0,,我是跟你同校的莫蒂\N{\ren}It's Morty. From school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.42,zh,,0,0,0,,嘿，莫蒂，你好吗？\N{\ren}Oh, hey, Morty. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:48.40,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是想说，你很棒\N{\ren}Um, I just want to say that you're really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:49.69,zh,,0,0,0,,我知道我们每次都抓不好时机\N{\ren}I know the timing never really worked out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:52.36,zh,,0,0,0,,但你真的很棒，我好想更了解你\N{\ren}but you're great, and I wish I got to know you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:54.20,zh,,0,0,0,,还真是突然\N{\ren}Oh. I mean... That's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:56.28,zh,,0,0,0,,对，抱歉，我只是…\N{\ren}Oh, uh, yeah, sorry. I guess I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.42,zh,,0,0,0,,不，你该早点说的\N{\ren}No, I just wish you said it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.47,zh,,0,0,0,,－什么？　－对，紧张\N{\ren}- What? - Yeah, I mean, being nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.14,zh,,0,0,0,,有时候其实很自私\N{\ren}is sort of selfish sometimes, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:03.93,zh,,0,0,0,,－对，有道理　－维生系统故障\N{\ren}- Yeah, that's a great point. - Life support systems failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:05.52,zh,,0,0,0,,你今晚有事吗？\N{\ren}Well, what are you doing tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:06.69,zh,,0,0,0,,－今晚？　－对\N{\ren}- Tonight? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.62,zh,,0,0,0,,想不想一起看电影之类的？\N{\ren}Do you want to watch a movie or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.79,zh,,0,0,0,,好，今晚，没问题\N{\ren}Um, yeah. Tonight. Sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:12.50,zh,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\ren}Holy shit. Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:13.75,zh,,0,0,0,,糟了，拜托…\N{\ren}Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:24.57,zh,,0,0,0,,－这是哪里？　－到家了，瑞克\N{\ren}- Where are we? - We're home, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:26.12,zh,,0,0,0,,我降落在海上\N{\ren}I landed us in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.12,zh,,0,0,0,,海？地球的海？\N{\ren}The ocean? The ocean on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:30.18,zh,,0,0,0,,－对，应该是　－这下完蛋了\N{\ren}- Uh, yeah, I guess so. - Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:32.81,zh,,0,0,0,,我们得离开，他妈的马上离开\N{\ren}Holy shit. We have to go. We have to go right fucking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.23,zh,,0,0,0,,－啥？　－你碰到海了\N{\ren}- What? - You touched the ocean, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:35.77,zh,,0,0,0,,－为什么不能…　－糟了，完蛋了…\N{\ren}- What's the big... - Oh, fuck. Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:36.94,zh,,0,0,0,,－怎么了？　－操\N{\ren}- What? - Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.58,zh,,0,0,0,,理查德，你亵渎了\N{\ren}Richard! You have desecrated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.76,zh,,0,0,0,,海陆神圣条约\N{\ren}the sacred treaty betwixt land and sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.97,zh,,0,0,0,,准备承受劲敌\N{\ren}Now face the wrath of your once and eternal foe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.73,zh,,0,0,0,,宁波先生的怒火\N{\ren}Mr. Nimbus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:52.20,zh,,0,0,0,,－不好意思，他是谁？　－我的劲敌\N{\ren}- Sorry. Who is that? - My... nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:54.03,zh,,0,0,0,,－什么？　－我的劲敌，好吗？\N{\ren}- What? - My fucking nemesis, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.50,zh,,0,0,0,,好，但他叫什么？\N{\ren}Okay, but what was his name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.46,zh,,0,0,0,,我是宁波先生\N{\ren}I am Mr. Nimbus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:58.72,zh,,0,0,0,,他会一直讲\N{\ren}He's gonna say that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:32.81,zh,,0,0,0,,等等，到底是谁要来？\N{\ren}W-Wait, so who is coming over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:35.11,zh,,0,0,0,,－好像说是劲敌？　－瑞克有劲敌？\N{\ren}- He said his nemesis. - Rick has a nemesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.74,zh,,0,0,0,,－好像是 －他提过那个人吗？\N{\ren}- I guess. - Has he mentioned him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:38.96,zh,,0,0,0,,我才要问你吧？我都没听说过\N{\ren}I was gonna ask you. First I'm hearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.84,zh,,0,0,0,,他是谁？魔术师？\N{\ren}Who is he? Like, a magic guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.22,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克是科学家，他是魔术师？\N{\ren}Rick's science, and he's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.34,zh,,0,0,0,,－他应该算是鱼？　－一条鱼\N{\ren}- He's, like... a fish? - A fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:46.01,zh,,0,0,0,,他不是鱼，他叫宁波先生\N{\ren}He's not a fish, he's Mr. Nimbus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.53,zh,,0,0,0,,他是海王兼混蛋\N{\ren}He's king of the ocean, and he's a piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.24,zh,,0,0,0,,你满意了吗，莫蒂？\N{\ren}Are you happy, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.66,zh,,0,0,0,,碰到海开心吗？\N{\ren}Are you happy you touched the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.71,zh,,0,0,0,,他随时会到，来帮我做准备\N{\ren}He's gonna be here any minute. Just help me smooth this over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.79,zh,,0,0,0,,否则他一定会造成更多麻烦\N{\ren}or this guy's gonna become more trouble than he's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:58.35,zh,,0,0,0,,嘿，我今晚无法帮你太多，瑞克\N{\ren}Um, hey, I don't know how much I can help out tonight, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.94,zh,,0,0,0,,洁西卡要来跟我一起看电影\N{\ren}Jessica's coming over, just to, like, watch a movie or something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:02.77,zh,,0,0,0,,但这是很棒的一步\N{\ren}but, y'know, that's a good step.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.44,zh,,0,0,0,,或许会有很好的发展，对吧？\N{\ren}That's a solid step to something, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.36,zh,,0,0,0,,真的没人在乎你下面，莫蒂\N{\ren}Truly, nobody cares about your dick, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:07.53,zh,,0,0,0,,你越快认清这点越好\N{\ren}The sooner you learn that, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.71,zh,,0,0,0,,你不希望我幸福\N{\ren}I think you just don't want me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.55,zh,,0,0,0,,想继续使唤我\N{\ren}'cause then I'll stop doing your crazy chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.18,zh,,0,0,0,,相信我，你搞出那场海洋闹剧\N{\ren}Trust me, after that ocean fuck-up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.64,zh,,0,0,0,,你别想多做任何事\N{\ren}you don't get to do anything crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:16.35,zh,,0,0,0,,我一边假装跟宁波谈和平条约时\N{\ren}While I bullshit my way through this peace summit treaty with Nimbus
