Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:25.67,zh,,0,0,0,,－我不喜欢　－好，什么？\N{\ren}- I don't love that. - Okay, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.63,zh,,0,0,0,,那当然，因为你们没性生活\N{\ren}Of course you don't. Cause you guys aren't getting any.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:32.36,zh,,0,0,0,,其实我们最近非常性积极\N{\ren}Actually, your father and I have been very sexpositive lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.86,zh,,0,0,0,,王医师建议我们多多尝试\N{\ren}- Eww. - Dr. Wong suggested we experiment.
