Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:37.91,zh,,0,0,0,,－一起看色情片　－好恶\N{\ren}- Together. - Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.38,zh,,0,0,0,,我不想从海里回来了\N{\ren}I might never come back from the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.88,zh,,0,0,0,,你得低调点，宝贝\N{\ren}You'll have to tone it down, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.93,zh,,0,0,0,,这些凡人承受不了\N{\ren}The squares can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:45.22,zh,,0,0,0,,你们的牙齿里都有自杀胶囊\N{\ren}There are suicide capsules in all of your teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.77,zh,,0,0,0,,可以用用，莫蒂\N{\ren}Do what you want with that. C'mon, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:47.90,zh,,0,0,0,,你负责处理酒\N{\ren}You're on booze duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.49,zh,,0,0,0,,好，宁波只喝高级货\N{\ren}Okay, Nimbus only drinks the good shit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.08,zh,,0,0,0,,所以把这酒丢进去\N{\ren}so just toss this whale-ass ocean wine in here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.54,zh,,0,0,0,,放个几世纪\N{\ren}and age it up a few centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.09,zh,,0,0,0,,在里面时间过得比较快吗？\N{\ren}So, time moves faster in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.30,zh,,0,0,0,,像纳尼亚一样吗？\N{\ren}Is it like a Narnia thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.90,zh,,0,0,0,,我不是信上帝的海狸，莫蒂\N{\ren}I'm not a beaver who believes in Jesus Christ, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:00.98,zh,,0,0,0,,但确实就像纳尼亚那样\N{\ren}But yeah, it's pretty much a Narnia thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.74,zh,,0,0,0,,－但洁西卡… －你只负责端酒\N{\ren}- Okay, but Jessica... - All you have to do is bring wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.87,zh,,0,0,0,,－我拜托过你什么吗？　－你…\N{\ren}- When do I ask you for anything? - When do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.08,zh,,0,0,0,,我好几年没完整上过一周的课了\N{\ren}I haven't been to a full week of school in years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.72,zh,,0,0,0,,我什么都不会，这是为了什么？\N{\ren}I don't know shit! And for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.43,zh,,0,0,0,,你到底有多少敌人？\N{\ren}How many enemies do you have to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.72,zh,,0,0,0,,为何老爱起冲突？\N{\ren}Why is everything a fight with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.18,zh,,0,0,0,,你要早点看清\N{\ren}You might want to learn this early, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.98,zh,,0,0,0,,－人生充满了冲突 －跟宁波先生吗？\N{\ren}- Life is a fight. - With Mr. Nimbus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.15,zh,,0,0,0,,你在笑我吗？\N{\ren}Are you makin' fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.83,zh,,0,0,0,,宁波先生是冷血下体杀手，莫蒂\N{\ren}Mr. Nimbus is an ice-cold dick killer, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.42,zh,,0,0,0,,我们走，那是他的魔法海洋号角\N{\ren}Okay, let's go. That's his magic ocean horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.78,zh,,0,0,0,,他是宁波先生吗？\N{\ren}Is that Mr. Nimbus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.24,zh,,0,0,0,,－宁波　－理查德\N{\ren}- Nimbus. - Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.62,zh,,0,0,0,,你气色真差\N{\ren}You look like ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.99,zh,,0,0,0,,速战速决吧\N{\ren}Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.51,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，就是他吗？\N{\ren}I'm sorry. This is the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.88,zh,,0,0,0,,－杰瑞　－等等，不\N{\ren}- Jerry... - Hold on. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.34,zh,,0,0,0,,你是上过星球的人\N{\ren}I've seen you fuck a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.77,zh,,0,0,0,,竟然怕他？\N{\ren}and this is the guy you're afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.52,zh,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个，瑞克\N{\ren}I like this one, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.52,zh,,0,0,0,,他很健全且狂野\N{\ren}He is unbroken. Untamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.12,zh,,0,0,0,,或许我们应该把牵绳拉紧一点\N{\ren}Perhaps he could use a firmer grip upon his leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.92,zh,,0,0,0,,好，够了，我要报警了\N{\ren}Okay, that's enough. I'm calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.08,zh,,0,0,0,,－没问题　－杰瑞\N{\ren}- Go ahead. - Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.17,zh,,0,0,0,,－我真的会　－我能控制警察\N{\ren}- I will! - Good. I control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.51,zh,,0,0,0,,－什么？　－能控制警察，杰瑞\N{\ren}- Excuse me? - He controls police, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.15,zh,,0,0,0,,对，我如果会相信就太蠢了\N{\ren}Right, that tracks. In Dumb World.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:01.49,zh,,0,0,0,,警察？ 有个淫荡海男在我家门口\N{\ren}Police? A strange horny ocean man is on my lawn.
