Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.13,zh,,0,0,0,,但我马上就要去拿酒来了\N{\ren}But... But... But I'll go get that wine right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.27,zh,,0,0,0,,但你已经这样说过两次了吧？\N{\ren}But you said were going to get it, like, twice already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.65,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，我现在真的要去拿了\N{\ren}I was, and I'm getting it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.99,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，是他\N{\ren}Holy shit, it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.43,zh,,0,0,0,,真是的，你们要我怎样？\N{\ren}God damn it! What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.80,zh,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\ren}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.36,zh,,0,0,0,,我们总算打败他了\N{\ren}We finally beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.62,zh,,0,0,0,,但我们要保持警觉，世事难料\N{\ren}But let's always remain vigilant, because you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.12,zh,,0,0,0,,他或许还会再来\N{\ren}He might be back one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:13.72,zh,,0,0,0,,好，纳尼亚，来吧，放马过来\N{\ren}Okay, Narnia! Let's go. Let's fucking go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.81,zh,,0,0,0,,结束了，那男孩不会再来了\N{\ren}It is over. The boy is not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.44,zh,,0,0,0,,他一定会的\N{\ren}He always comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:22.78,zh,,0,0,0,,你害我们赔上了人生还有未来，只为了一个虚构故事\N{\ren}You have wasted our lives, our very futures, on a fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.83,zh,,0,0,0,,－一个谎言　－我确实看到了\N{\ren}- A lie! - I know what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.09,zh,,0,0,0,,你什么都没看到\N{\ren}You saw nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.18,zh,,0,0,0,,蠢孩子\N{\ren}You are a foolish boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:34.36,zh,,0,0,0,,勇于看见真相的人\N{\ren}Those called fools are the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.54,zh,,0,0,0,,才会被骂蠢\N{\ren}brave enough to see the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.85,zh,,0,0,0,,告诉我，父亲\N{\ren}Tell me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.10,zh,,0,0,0,,我还很蠢吗？\N{\ren}Am I a fool now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.79,zh,,0,0,0,,我出生于这些石块的制造地\N{\ren}I was born in the pits that made these stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:09.92,zh,,0,0,0,,我花很久时间建造这座谎言圣殿\N{\ren}I lost my years building a temple to a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.13,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我就把说谎当成我的能力\N{\ren}So, I made lies my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.72,zh,,0,0,0,,能力其实就是我们…\N{\ren}And what is power, but a lie we...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.07,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，是真的…\N{\ren}Oh, shit, he's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.70,zh,,0,0,0,,是真的，我搞错了\N{\ren}He's real! I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.20,zh,,0,0,0,,大错特错，神是…\N{\ren}I was so wrong! God is re...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.39,zh,,0,0,0,,服务真棒，我会给很多小费\N{\ren}Wow. Impeccable service. Big tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.28,zh,,0,0,0,,我比较喜欢另一个\N{\ren}I liked your other one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.90,zh,,0,0,0,,他叫什么吗？凯尔吗？\N{\ren}What was his name? Kyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.07,zh,,0,0,0,,－什么？　－没事\N{\ren}- What? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:49.79,zh,,0,0,0,,我们可以快点签约吗？\N{\ren}Can we just sign this thing and go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.42,zh,,0,0,0,,－洁西卡，真抱歉　－没关系\N{\ren}- Jessica, I'm so sorry. - I mean, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.72,zh,,0,0,0,,你才离开几分钟而已\N{\ren}You were only gone like a couple minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.01,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，你还好吗？\N{\ren}Morty, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:57.68,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，洁西卡\N{\ren}I'm... I'm sorry, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.65,zh,,0,0,0,,我们每次都搞砸，对吧？\N{\ren}We just never seem to get it right, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.32,zh,,0,0,0,,是啊，的确如此\N{\ren}No, I guess we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.82,zh,,0,0,0,,但我很高兴你打电话给我\N{\ren}But I'm glad you called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.54,zh,,0,0,0,,我们可以重来\N{\ren}Maybe we can start over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.13,zh,,0,0,0,,这次别再搞砸了\N{\ren}get it right this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.92,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我也想这样\N{\ren}Yeah. I'd... I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.09,zh,,0,0,0,,谢谢你拿酒来\N{\ren}Thanks for bringing the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.39,zh,,0,0,0,,非常值得\N{\ren}Totally worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.19,zh,,0,0,0,,需要开瓶器吗？\N{\ren}Do we need an opener?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.57,zh,,0,0,0,,我去拿\N{\ren}Oh. I'll... I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:20.08,zh,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢签约\N{\ren}Mmm. I do so love to sign upon the dotted line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.08,zh,,0,0,0,,－要签了吗？　－没错\N{\ren}- Shall we? - Jesus Christ, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:24.64,zh,,0,0,0,,你的证人是谁？我的证人是这只鱿鱼\N{\ren}And who is your witness? My witness is the squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.56,zh,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢海洋世界主题，对吧？\N{\ren}Really proud of this SeaWorld theme, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.65,zh,,0,0,0,,快去找证人，别怪到我头上\N{\ren}Hey, just get a witness, man. Don't make this about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:32.61,zh,,0,0,0,,或许他没有值得托付生命的人\N{\ren}Or perhaps, Richard has no one with whom he can trust his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.79,zh,,0,0,0,,除了我以外，没有人真正了解他\N{\ren}Who truly knows him, save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.30,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，我去找人，天啊\N{\ren}Fine! I'll get someone. Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.80,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，过来，我需要你做件鸟事\N{\ren}Morty! C'mere. I need you for some bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.64,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克，我达成你的每一项要求了\N{\ren}Look, Rick, I've done everything you've asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.44,zh,,0,0,0,,我能好好陪我女朋友吗？\N{\ren}Can I just have some time with my girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.61,zh,,0,0,0,,女朋友？\N{\ren}Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.82,zh,,0,0,0,,她不是…\N{\ren}I mean, she's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.95,zh,,0,0,0,,我们接吻了，但我想慢慢来\N{\ren}We kissed, but I'm just trying to take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.92,zh,,0,0,0,,不可以太操之过急，懂吗？\N{\ren}You gotta give these things time to breathe, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.90,zh,,0,0,0,,你知道你的特别之处吗，亚当？\N{\ren}Do you know why you're special, Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.82,zh,,0,0,0,,－因为我是旅行者？ －对\N{\ren}- Because I am The Traveler? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.11,zh,,0,0,0,,你会穿越那扇门\N{\ren}You will be the one to pass through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.92,zh,,0,0,0,,你会终结我们的痛苦\N{\ren}You will be the one to end our pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.21,zh,,0,0,0,,那我的痛苦呢，妈？\N{\ren}But, Mother, what about my pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.59,zh,,0,0,0,,你的痛苦会解放我们\N{\ren}Your pain shall set us free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.35,zh,,0,0,0,,该开始了\N{\ren}It is time to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.37,zh,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\ren}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.37,zh,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.98,zh,,0,0,0,,－你还没准备好 －拜托，妈\N{\ren}- You are not ready. - Please, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.98,zh,,0,0,0,,你以为他会放过你吗？\N{\ren}Do you think he will show you mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.61,zh,,0,0,0,,看他对我们做了什么？\N{\ren}Like he did to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.82,zh,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.66,zh,,0,0,0,,有人需要什么吗？\N{\ren}Does anyone need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.09,zh,,0,0,0,,－宁波要什么吗？ －天啊\N{\ren}- Does Nimbus need anything? - Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.92,zh,,0,0,0,,别评断我们，我们夫妻要一起成长\N{\ren}Don't judge. We're growing as a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.15,zh,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样？\N{\ren}Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.44,zh,,0,0,0,,为了未来\N{\ren}For the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.12,zh,,0,0,0,,你竟然想暗杀宁波？\N{\ren}You dare assassinate Nimbus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.70,zh,,0,0,0,,－抱歉，等等，他是谁？ －还没轮到你，老兄\N{\ren}- Sorry, wait. Who is that? - Get in line, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:10.94,zh,,0,0,0,,真是浪费\N{\ren}Such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.31,zh,,0,0,0,,妈？\N{\ren}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.83,zh,,0,0,0,,洁西卡\N{\ren}Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.55,zh,,0,0,0,,你就是非碰海不可\N{\ren}You just had to touch the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.15,zh,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，我没时间…\N{\ren}Shut up! There isn't time to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.11,zh,,0,0,0,,全都搞砸了，被你搞砸了\N{\ren}It's all fucked, and you fucked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.96,zh,,0,0,0,,你提早来了\N{\ren}- Huh? - You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.68,zh,,0,0,0,,这里是哪里？\N{\ren}Wh... What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.47,zh,,0,0,0,,是终点也是起点\N{\ren}The end. But also, a beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.73,zh,,0,0,0,,－每个终点都是起点，对吧？ －后退\N{\ren}- Isn't every end a beginning? - Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.15,zh,,0,0,0,,别跟我说些日舞科幻鬼话\N{\ren}I don't want your stripped down, Sundance sci-fi bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:44.12,zh,,0,0,0,,－洁西卡在哪？　－洁西卡\N{\ren}- Where's Jessica? - Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.87,zh,,0,0,0,,那是她的名字，对吧？\N{\ren}That was her name, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.92,zh,,0,0,0,,谢了，莫蒂，我都忘记了\N{\ren}Thank you, Morty. I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:50.97,zh,,0,0,0,,对了，你可以\N{\ren}Oh, right. You'll be needing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:53.18,zh,,0,0,0,,用这个酿酒\N{\ren}For the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.12,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，我们骗到他了\N{\ren}Oh, shit, we got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.91,zh,,0,0,0,,你敢相信他被这些鬼话骗了吗？\N{\ren}Can you believe he bought that fuckin' tree bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.29,zh,,0,0,0,,我们骗到他了\N{\ren}We fuckin' got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:08.44,zh,,0,0,0,,非常好，想跟亚特兰提斯开战，就顺你意\N{\ren}Very well. If you seek war with Atlantis, you shall have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.23,zh,,0,0,0,,我之前上美人鱼时\N{\ren}Oh, I've already been to war with Atlantis
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:11.69,zh,,0,0,0,,就已经开战了\N{\ren}when I DDay'd that Mermaid Puss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.46,zh,,0,0,0,,我就知道是你，准备离场车队\N{\ren}I knew that was you! Prepare my exit parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.50,zh,,0,0,0,,跟你爱的干燥陆地道别吧\N{\ren}Say goodbye to your precious dry land
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.72,zh,,0,0,0,,这里很快就会变湿，超级湿\N{\ren}for soon, it will be wet! Wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.80,zh,,0,0,0,,全球暖化已经弄湿陆地了，混蛋\N{\ren}Yeah, global warming is already doing that, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:24.49,zh,,0,0,0,,尽管来吧，让我们变得更湿一点\N{\ren}But sure, yeah, go for it. Make us slightly more wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:27.24,zh,,0,0,0,,－你把我当笑话？　－对，没错\N{\ren}- Am I a joke to you? - Yes, you are a fucking joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.24,zh,,0,0,0,,你烂透了，你一直都很烂\N{\ren}You fucking suck! You've always sucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.29,zh,,0,0,0,,知道我们为何好几年没打仗吗？\N{\ren}You know why we haven't fought in years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.54,zh,,0,0,0,,因为你很可笑，我不需要你了\N{\ren}'Cause you're an embarrassment to me, and I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.43,zh,,0,0,0,,我不靠别人，都在跟\N{\ren}I don't need anybody. All I do is eat ass
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.56,zh,,0,0,0,,任天堂做爱，每一天\N{\ren}and 69 Nintendos, bro. Every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.61,zh,,0,0,0,,或许你会讨厌我，是因为只有我\N{\ren}Or maybe, you hate me because I am the only man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.03,zh,,0,0,0,,知道你变得多惨\N{\ren}to see how far you have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.70,zh,,0,0,0,,我曾经害怕你，尊敬你\N{\ren}I used to fear you. Respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:47.72,zh,,0,0,0,,但我现在只会可怜你这可悲酒鬼\N{\ren}Now all that's left is pity for a sad, drunk shell of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:50.26,zh,,0,0,0,,你不敢承认自己有多寂寞\N{\ren}too afraid to see how alone he truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.81,zh,,0,0,0,,如果戴安还活着，她会怎么…\N{\ren}If Diane were alive today, what would she think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.37,zh,,0,0,0,,少跟我讲另一个时空的背景故事\N{\ren}Don't fucking establish canonical backstory with me, you Red Lob...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.42,zh,,0,0,0,,很好，你醒了\N{\ren}Oh, good. You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.30,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是拿了些酒，我都道歉了\N{\ren}I just took some wine! I said I was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.26,zh,,0,0,0,,你们有什么毛病？\N{\ren}What the fuck is wrong with you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.31,zh,,0,0,0,,我已经思考这件事好几世纪了\N{\ren}I have been asking that for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.36,zh,,0,0,0,,他们建造我是为了研究你，莫蒂\N{\ren}I was created to study you, Morty. To know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.74,zh,,0,0,0,,但我越仔细看，就越不认得自己\N{\ren}But the closer I looked, the more I do not recognize myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.54,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我其实没时间…\N{\ren}Uh, yeah, man, I really don't have time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:14.25,zh,,0,0,0,,如果没有你，我们会是什么人？\N{\ren}I have often wondered... who would we be without you, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.52,zh,,0,0,0,,我们除了恨意还有什么？\N{\ren}Are we anything beyond our hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:19.73,zh,,0,0,0,,她来的时候，我以为她会是答案\N{\ren}And when she came, I thought she would be the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.15,zh,,0,0,0,,被冻结在时间内，永远沉睡着\N{\ren}Frozen in time. Forever asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:25.21,zh,,0,0,0,,我们不懂她的意义，就把她隐藏起来\N{\ren}We could not understand her purpose, so we hid her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.05,zh,,0,0,0,,我们为什么都要隐藏…\N{\ren}Why do we always hide the truths we...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.97,zh,,0,0,0,,我不在乎，放了她\N{\ren}I don't give a shit, nerd! Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.76,zh,,0,0,0,,我干吗复制生殖器？\N{\ren}Why did I clone myself genitals?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.22,zh,,0,0,0,,我不在乎，动作快\N{\ren}- Ow! Ooh! - I don't care, bitch! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.18,zh,,0,0,0,,－混蛋　－我就是混蛋\N{\ren}- Asshole! - Yeah, I guess I am an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.78,zh,,0,0,0,,有时候就得当混蛋\N{\ren}Y'know, sometimes, you gotta be an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.58,zh,,0,0,0,,－这是我外公教我的　－好吧…\N{\ren}- My grandpa taught me that. - Okay, okay, okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:42.96,zh,,0,0,0,,－莫蒂？　－洁西卡\N{\ren}- Morty? - Hey, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:44.97,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，你一定睡得很熟，对吧？\N{\ren}Wow. Must've been some nap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.27,zh,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么称呼这些东西\N{\ren}Is that, ooze or... I'm not sure what to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.02,zh,,0,0,0,,看起来像分泌物\N{\ren}It looks like ooze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.94,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我们之后再聊\N{\ren}Okay. We can catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.09,zh,,0,0,0,,什么…\N{\ren}What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.31,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克\N{\ren}Rick! Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.81,zh,,0,0,0,,－死龙虾 －瑞克\N{\ren}- ...obster motherfucker. - Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.28,zh,,0,0,0,,－管他的，我在干吗？　－救命\N{\ren}- Screw this. What am I even doing? - Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.20,zh,,0,0,0,,你要去哪？\N{\ren}Where are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.75,zh,,0,0,0,,快回来 我会把陆地变湿\N{\ren}Come back here. I'm going to make the land wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.67,zh,,0,0,0,,我倒想亲眼瞧瞧\N{\ren}Y'know what, I'd love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:13.21,zh,,0,0,0,,放马过来，你要做什么都好\N{\ren}Do it! God, do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.60,zh,,0,0,0,,但别再拿我当借口了\N{\ren}Just don't use me as an excuse anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.73,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克\N{\ren}Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.53,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，真火爆\N{\ren}Wow. That was intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:22.11,zh,,0,0,0,,－你压力很大吗？ －我们签了文件\N{\ren}- You look stressed. - We signed the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.99,zh,,0,0,0,,－我得走了 －你们有我们的电话\N{\ren}- I must go. - Your people have our number!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:26.05,zh,,0,0,0,,那只海星不是说有礼物篮吗？\N{\ren}Your starfish mentioned some kind of basket?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.55,zh,,0,0,0,,－莫蒂，能不能别…　－停止…\N{\ren}- Jesus, Morty. - Stop! No, no! Not today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.10,zh,,0,0,0,,你不能就…\N{\ren}Can't you go one day without...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.93,zh,,0,0,0,,－什么…　－我搞砸了，好吗？\N{\ren}- What the... - I fucked it up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.85,zh,,0,0,0,,没关系，莫蒂，你就是这样\N{\ren}It's okay, Morty. That's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:36.29,zh,,0,0,0,,我来拯救一切，带你们回家\N{\ren}Now, lemme deus ex machina this shit and let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.92,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，为何大家都变机械鸟了？\N{\ren}God, why does everyone go cyberpunk bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.34,zh,,0,0,0,,真无趣\N{\ren}So fuckin' hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.27,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，还真酷\N{\ren}Oh, shit. Well, that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.22,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，我们好像有点完蛋了\N{\ren}Okay, we might be a little fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.23,zh,,0,0,0,,你以为我会让你死吗，理查德？\N{\ren}Did you think I would let you die alone, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:17.11,zh,,0,0,0,,我是宁波先生\N{\ren}I am Mr. Nimbus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:25.30,zh,,0,0,0,,你还有时间看电影吗？\N{\ren}Wow. You still got time for that movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.39,zh,,0,0,0,,对，时间\N{\ren}Yes. Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:30.60,zh,,0,0,0,,我有很多时间，无尽的时间\N{\ren}I had nothing but time. Endless time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.07,zh,,0,0,0,,一开始只有疯狂\N{\ren}At first, it was madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.41,zh,,0,0,0,,然后是启示\N{\ren}Then, enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.04,zh,,0,0,0,,然后又是疯狂\N{\ren}Then madness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.54,zh,,0,0,0,,但这或许是好事\N{\ren}But perhaps it was a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.59,zh,,0,0,0,,我看到了时间的生命\N{\ren}I could see the life of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:45.36,zh,,0,0,0,,正当我见证着时间悲惨的那一面\N{\ren}And as I watched the life of time in all its fleeting, terrible light
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.53,zh,,0,0,0,,我陷入了沉思，我有活过吗？\N{\ren}I wondered, had I lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.82,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是其他人故事中的物件吗？\N{\ren}Was I just the object in another's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.58,zh,,0,0,0,,我就仅此而已？这点能改变吗？\N{\ren}Was that all I ever was? Could I be more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:55.64,zh,,0,0,0,,我有非常多的时间，却没有答案\N{\ren}I had nothing but time, and still no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.77,zh,,0,0,0,,没有意义的时间就像是监牢\N{\ren}Time without purpose is a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.02,zh,,0,0,0,,我看到了永恒的思想\N{\ren}I have glimpsed into the mind of eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.90,zh,,0,0,0,,或是神的思想\N{\ren}perhaps the mind of God
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.95,zh,,0,0,0,,但我只找到寂静\N{\ren}and found nothing but silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.50,zh,,0,0,0,,我们还是当朋友就好\N{\ren}I think we should just be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.09,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我能理解\N{\ren}Oh, yeah. I... I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.93,zh,,0,0,0,,我们错过了时机\N{\ren}Guess we missed our moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:14.14,zh,,0,0,0,,对，但我们都会\N{\ren}Yes. But there will be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.74,zh,,0,0,0,,有其他时机\N{\ren}For both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.95,zh,,0,0,0,,再见了，莫蒂\N{\ren}Goodbye, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.04,zh,,0,0,0,,－嘿，你好吗？ －滚，我是时间之神\N{\ren}- Hey, how's it going? - fuck off! I'm a time god.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.75,zh,,0,0,0,,我又跟你一同作战了，理查德\N{\ren}Fighting by your side again, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.43,zh,,0,0,0,,－感觉很…　－没错\N{\ren}- It was, uh... - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.02,zh,,0,0,0,,那就不用签条约了\N{\ren}Then there is no treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:27.27,zh,,0,0,0,,我们停战\N{\ren}Because there is no war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:29.94,zh,,0,0,0,,宁波，你人真好\N{\ren}Aw, Nimbus. That's... That's really chill of you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:33.15,zh,,0,0,0,,理查德，你在成为我的宿敌之前\N{\ren}Richard, before you were my greatest enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.17,zh,,0,0,0,,你是我唯一的朋友\N{\ren}you were my only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.50,zh,,0,0,0,,－爷爷，我弄到贝壳了 －操\N{\ren}- Grandpa, I got the shell! - Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:39.01,zh,,0,0,0,,－听着，宁波　－王八蛋\N{\ren}- Okay, Nimbus, look... - You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:40.55,zh,,0,0,0,,－叛徒 －拿武器来，莫蒂\N{\ren}- Betrayal! - My weapons, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.05,zh,,0,0,0,,－我用光了 －爷爷\N{\ren}- I used them all! - Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.31,zh,,0,0,0,,怎么办？\N{\ren}Wait, Grandpa, what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.82,zh,,0,0,0,,－贝壳在我这里，我要吹吗？要吗？ －别\N{\ren}- I have the shell. Should I blow it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.07,zh,,0,0,0,,我直接吹好了\N{\ren}Is that... I'm just gonna blow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:48.74,zh,,0,0,0,,－不要吹，砸烂它 －搞什么？\N{\ren}- Don't blow it! Destroy the horn! - What the hell, Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:50.41,zh,,0,0,0,,要把贝壳砸烂\N{\ren}You were supposed to destroy the horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:52.13,zh,,0,0,0,,我怎么会知道？\N{\ren}How was I supposed to know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.36,zh,,0,0,0,,警察，把这人渣关进牢里\N{\ren}Police! Take this piece of shit to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.53,zh,,0,0,0,,我说过了\N{\ren}I told... I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.49,zh,,0,0,0,,他是冷血下体杀手\N{\ren}He's an ice-cold dick killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.87,zh,,0,0,0,,宁波\N{\ren}Nimbus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.00,zh,,0,0,0,,等等，他怎么…\N{\ren}Wait. So, how can he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:08.18,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，桑美，他是宁波\N{\ren}Jesus, Summer. He's Mr. Nimbus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:09.68,zh,,0,0,0,,他能控制警察\N{\ren}He controls the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:44.82,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，太多安全语就失去意义了\N{\ren}Jer, I think more than one safe word sort of defeats the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.08,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是希望\N{\ren}I know, I just wanna make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.87,zh,,0,0,0,,我们能有机会喊停\N{\ren}we have every opportunity to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:49.75,zh,,0,0,0,,但我很期待\N{\ren}Super excited about it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.25,zh,,0,0,0,,我也很期待\N{\ren}Me too, so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.52,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，我们是真的想这么做吗？\N{\ren}Jerry, are we doing this because we both want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:57.15,zh,,0,0,0,,还是我们以为对方想这么做？\N{\ren}Or because it's what we think the other one wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:59.11,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是想证明我很爱你\N{\ren}I just wanted to prove that I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:01.07,zh,,0,0,0,,－愿意为你做这种事 －我也是\N{\ren}- I would do this for you! - Same!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.74,zh,,0,0,0,,我们拿完奖品就走吧，不要犯下大错\N{\ren}Let's take that prize and get out before we make a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.09,zh,,0,0,0,,后悔了？\N{\ren}Getting cold feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:09.01,zh,,0,0,0,,不，别告诉瑞克\N{\ren}No. Please don't tell Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.94,zh,,0,0,0,,－他不会懂的　－会，他会懂的\N{\ren}- He wouldn't understand. - Yes, he would.
